{"tid":1281243,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"90分鐘講座 送5日4夜酒店旅行係呃人 小心！！","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:23:01.000Z","uid":24265,"like":8,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1551e2da797f65dfd10c3ebd4c70366391a014cc","tid":1281243,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"自問好撚精明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有條撚樣岩岩打黎話之前做過問卷<br />\n又送呢送路咁咪聽下佢講乜<br />\n佢個手法係幾好 同你吹下水閒話家常<br />\n然後就話聽日去TST 聽個講座就會送你5日4夜機票連酒店<br />\n<br />\n然後傾撚左成個鐘 之後就約左聽日去佢公司聽講座拎禮品啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一收線就即刻上網check下 屌你老母真係呃鳩人<br />\n相信好撚多毒撚會落搭<br />\n<br />\n小心！小心！！小心<br />\n唔洗屌我 我係貪小便宜先信<br />\n想俾多啲人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撚毒一聽到女人聲就以為有女想溝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫手傳出去 唔知有無其他人中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9ASAPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9ASAPn.png&h=b2101244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdkfyA9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdkfyA9.png&h=82497fb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"641feb5a57ab2ea0a6d52b21ac7a2d4e992b52e4","tid":1281243,"uid":24265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5fd4844e31c2d1e074d50c7004f6d0f19fd940a0","tid":1281243,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"aac90171fcda761c6d1193cf0ec5db8634594b11","tid":1281243,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0972816668d52d62f0a1ccdbced9780f23ebcaa7","tid":1281243,"uid":2